Maintainer: Debian X Strike Force <debian-x@lists.debian.org>
Uploaders: David Nusinow <dnusinow@debian.org>, Jamey Sharp <sharpone@debian.org>, Josh Triplett <josh@freedesktop.org>, Julien Cristau <jcristau@debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0), libx11-dev (>= 1:0.99.2), libxext-dev (>= 1:0.99.1), x11proto-randr-dev (>= 1.2), x11proto-render-dev, libxrender-dev (>= 1:0.9.0-2), pkg-config, quilt
Standards-Version: 3.7.3
Vcs-Git: git://git.debian.org/git/pkg-xorg/lib/libxrandr
